{"ja431:0.1":"Jataka ","ja431:0.2":"Navakanipata ","ja431:0.3":"Gijjhavagga ","ja431:0.4":"5. Haritacajataka ","ja431:1.1":"“Sutam metam mahabrahme, ","ja431:1.2":"kame bhunjati harito; ","ja431:1.3":"Kaccetam vacanam tuccham, ","ja431:1.4":"kacci suddho iriyyasi”. ","ja431:2.1":"“Evametam maharaja, ","ja431:2.2":"yatha te vacanam sutam; ","ja431:2.3":"Kummaggam patipannosmi, ","ja431:2.4":"mohaneyyesu mucchito”. ","ja431:3.1":"“Adu panna kimatthiya, ","ja431:3.2":"nipuna sadhucintini; ","ja431:3.3":"Yaya uppatitam ragam, ","ja431:3.4":"kim mano na vinodaye”. ","ja431:4.1":"“Cattarome maharaja, ","ja431:4.2":"loke atibala bhusa; ","ja431:4.3":"Rago doso mado moho, ","ja431:4.4":"yattha panna na gadhati”. ","ja431:5.1":"“Araha silasampanno, ","ja431:5.2":"suddho carati harito; ","ja431:5.3":"Medhavi pandito ceva, ","ja431:5.4":"iti no sammato bhavam”. ","ja431:6.1":"“Medhavinampi himsanti, ","ja431:6.2":"isim dhammagune ratam; ","ja431:6.3":"Vitakka papaka raja, ","ja431:6.4":"subha ragupasamhita”. ","ja431:7.1":"“Uppannayam sarirajo, ","ja431:7.2":"Rago vannavidusano tava; ","ja431:7.3":"Tam pajaha bhaddamatthu te, ","ja431:7.4":"Bahunnasi medhavisammato”. ","ja431:8.1":"“Te andhakarake kame, ","ja431:8.2":"Bahudukkhe mahavise; ","ja431:8.3":"Tesam mulam gavesissam, ","ja431:8.4":"Checcham ragam sabandhanam”. ","ja431:9.1":"“Idam vatvana harito, ","ja431:9.2":"isi saccaparakkamo; ","ja431:9.3":"Kamaragam virajetva, ","ja431:9.4":"brahmalokupago ahu”ti. ","ja431:10.1":"Haritacajatakam pancamam. "}